Observable
public class TreeDragSource
extends DragSource

A DragSource implementation for Trees.

When using a binder, the data being passed to the target is not the list of selected models. The data will be list of TreeModels. For each selected model, TreeStore.getModelState(ModelData) will be called. This ensures that the data being passed reflects the model actual data as the data in stored within the store, and not he model itself.
